metadata.name: SUNDAY IS MY DAY
metadata.description:
SUNDAY IS MY DAY (2022) is part of the SUNDAY Collection. Because Sunday is the best day of the week. Artwork has a physical base, Oil-on-canvas made by Joos Art.(Belgium) 

Digital remastered by Diggy Fred with BeFunky Photo Editor & PhotoMosh software for Glitchy effect. 

GIF 11,3 MB 
640x590
